    "summary": "Dedicated, result driven Business/Customer Intelligence specialist, focused on the financial and manufacturing industry and within these industries experience with a wide variety of business applications. A good team builder and currently looking for new challenges.\n \nOver 20 years of professional experience in the Business Intelligence (BI) and Data Warehousing (DW) field. \nWorked as a managing consultant for Atos (Origin) International in Brussels and was among other things the BI team manager, a principal consultant and/or project manager for multinational customers. Goal of most projects was the development and delivery of BI/DWH applications/systems; build with/on a SAS, SAP or Oracle environment or a combination of these. Common functional application domains were: Sales (profitability analysis, forecasting), Finance (consolidation and reporting), Analytical Customer Relationship Management and  Logistics (Supply Chain and Planning systems). \n\nWas at the ING Bank one of the initiators of the development of an (analytical) Customer Relationship Management system to optimize the Direct Marketing Process, a system that has survived many years and still is the base for the tools they are using today. \nDuring entire career developed a good understanding of the organizational impact when new ICT tools are introduced.\n\nSpecialties: DWH/BI architecture\nProject Management\nBusiness Intelligence\nCustomer Intelligence",
